en â€™92 #6 2016. Publisher: Marvel)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1905\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1905\" data-attachment-id=\"1905\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/alti-firmansyah-srikandi-indonesia-yang-mendunia/attachment/xmen927body-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Xmen927body-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Xmen92#7body-6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(X-Men â€™92 #6 2016. Publisher: Marvel)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Xmen927body-6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Xmen927body-6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1905\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Xmen927body-6.jpg\" alt=\"(X-Men â€™92 #6 2016. Publisher: Marvel)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Xmen927body-6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Xmen927body-6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1905\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(X-Men â€™92 #6 2016. Publisher: Marvel)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Saat ini lagi sibuk bikin komik apa Mbak? Kolaborasi sama siapa writer nya?</strong></p>\n<p>AF: Januari 2017 kemarin aku dapet kesempatan kolaborasi samaÂ Christopher HastingsÂ untuk komikÂ Gwenpool. Selain itu, dalam 20 halaman komik ini, aku kedapetan 15 halaman dan 5 halamannya itu artistnya adalahÂ Gurihiru; <em>main artist</em> dalam serial Gwenpool ini.</p>\n<p>Idih, keren amat nih Mbak Alti.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1912\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1912\" data-attachment-id=\"1912\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/alti-firmansyah-srikandi-indonesia-yang-mendunia/attachment/bod2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bod2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"bod2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gwenpool #13 2017 (previewsworld.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bod2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bod2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1912\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bod2.jpg\" alt=\"Gwenpool #13 2017 (previewsworld.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bod2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/bod2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1912\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gwenpool #13 2017 (previewsworld.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1906\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1906\" data-attachment-id=\"1906\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/alti-firmansyah-srikandi-indonesia-yang-mendunia/attachment/gwenpool132017body-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gwenpool#132017body-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1906\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-1.jpg\" alt=\"(Gwenpool #13 2017. Publisher: Marvel)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1906\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Gwenpool #13 2017. Publisher: Marvel)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1907\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1907\" data-attachment-id=\"1907\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/alti-firmansyah-srikandi-indonesia-yang-mendunia/attachment/gwenpool132017body-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gwenpool#132017body-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1907\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Gwenpool #13 2017. Publisher: Marvel)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Gwenpool132017body-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1907\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Gwenpool #13 2017. Publisher: Marvel)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>MM: Gimana tanggapan Mbak Alti tentang pertumbuhan dunia komik di Indonesia, mulai dari Mbak berkecimpung di dunia komik sampai sekarang?</strong></p>\n<p>AF: Yang saya lihat perkembangannya cukup menarik, karena generasi sekarang lebih berani untuk membuat cerita yang di luar <em>mainstream</em> dengan <em>style</em> yang unik juga. Selain itu juga <em>artist</em> masa kini jenius dalam menuangkan ide bagaimana memvisualisasikan unsur Indonesia ke dalam wadah komik, tanpa terkesan jadul dan tetap menarik untuk dibaca oleh generasi masa kini.<br />\n<strong>MM: Dengan munculnya komik digital, apa tanggapan Mbak Alti tentang dunia perkomikan?</strong></p>\n<p>AF: Sangat mempermudah dan menghibur. Di samping kita bisa baca komik <em>online</em> yang baru-baru dan <em>fresh looking</em>, kita juga bisa baca komik lama sepertiÂ Dragon BallÂ atauÂ Slam DunkÂ di media <em>online</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>MM: Boleh sharing sedikit nggak Mbak, minta masukan atau pesan-pesan buat komikus yang baru mau mulai serius menjadikan hobi ngomik jadi profesi?Â </strong></p>\n<p>AF: Dengan banyaknya sosmed dan teknologi canggih seperti sekarang ini, <em>artist</em> luar negeri maupun dalam negeri yang karyanya amat sangat menarik bisa di-<em>follow</em>, dan bisa dapet berita ter-<em>update</em> dari kegiatan mereka. <em>Style</em> yang bermacam-macam bisa dikumpulkan, dipelajari, dan dijadiin bahan referensi. Film kartun/animasi juga bisa dijadiin sebagai bahan referensi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1908\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1908\" data-attachment-id=\"1908\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/alti-firmansyah-srikandi-indonesia-yang-mendunia/attachment/xmen929body-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Xmen929body-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Xmen92#9body-7\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(X-Men â€™92 #9 2016. Publisher: Marvel)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/upload